'''''Sierra's 3-D Helicopter Simulator''''' is a 1987 video game published by [[Sierra On-Line]].

==Gameplay==
''Sierra's 3-D Helicopter Simulator'' is a combat helicopter simulation in which head-to-head play is available via modem.<ref name="CGW44"/>

==Reception==
M. Evan Brooks reviewed the game for ''[[Computer Gaming World]]'', and stated that "While 3-D Helicopter Simulator offers an interesting flight experience and a challenging two player modem game, the game is somewhat predictable as a solitaire combat simulator."<ref name="CGW44">{{cite magazine |last=Brooks |first=M. Evan |title=Choppers!: Evan's Fighting Gunships |magazine=Computer Gaming World |date=February 1988 |volume=1 |issue=44 |pages=15}}</ref>

